@UTF8
@Begin
@Languages:	eng
@Participants:	CHI Child
@ID:	eng|corpus|CHI|||||Child|||
@Comment:	ERROR: Replacement word cannot be omission (0-prefixed)
@Comment:	Invalid: "hello [: 0word]" - Replacement contains 0word (omission)
@Comment:	Semantic rule: Words in replacement must be real words
@Comment:	Real words exclude: 0word, &~nonword, &-filler, &+fragment
*CHI:	hello [: 0word] .
@End
